    "body": "Newport, Rhode Island is one of New England's most beloved destinations — and the Jane Pickens Film + Event Center is one of its crown jewels. This stunning historic theater is the kind of room where every show feels like an event, and we're thrilled to be performing there.\n\nEven better: Jane Pickens Film + Event Center, in partnership with Spectacle Live, is running a special all-in ticket deal — just $25 for select shows, including The British Invasion Years.\n\nFor a night of live '60s music in one of Newport's most beautiful venues, $25 is a genuine steal. This is the kind of deal that fills a room fast, so don't sit on it.\n\nGrab your tickets through the Jane Pickens website or Spectacle Live. New England audiences — this one is for you.",
