    "body": "November is shaping up to be a big month on the road for The British Invasion Years, and we couldn't be more excited.\n\nHere's the rundown:\n\n**November 7** — New England. Tickets are on sale now and already moving fast. If you've been waiting, stop waiting.\n\n**November 12** — Irwin, PA. We're heading back to the Pittsburgh area for what promises to be a fantastic night at the Lamp Theatre.\n\n**November 18** — Delray Beach, FL. We're bringing the British Invasion south for a night in one of South Florida's great live music communities.\n\nThree cities, three shows, three opportunities to experience the '60s the way they were meant to sound. Get your tickets early — shows at this level don't stay available for long.",
