    "body": "The Levoy Theatre in Millville, New Jersey is one of the jewels of the South Jersey performing arts scene — a beautifully restored early 20th-century venue with incredible acoustics and an atmosphere that perfectly complements the music of the 1960s.\n\nThis performance video captures The British Invasion Years in full flight. The band — composed of musicians who have played with and opened for some of the biggest stars in music — delivers a show that goes far beyond standard tribute territory.\n\nWhat you'll see is authenticity: the arrangements, the tone, the energy, and the sheer joy of playing music that defined a generation. The crowd response says everything.\n\nIf you haven't seen this show live yet, let this video be your motivation. Check the tour dates page for upcoming appearances near you.",
